    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "叨叨令湛湛青天不可欺，未曾举意吾先知。善恶到头终有报，只争来早与来迟。吾乃海神是也，连日巡查海盗，未曾归殿。今有莱阳敫桂英，到殿诉冤。鬼判，肃整威仪者！啊！苦吓！恨漫漫天无际，阿呀王魁吓，闪赚人无靠无依。俺向那海神灵，诉出从前誓，勾取那辜恩贼。奴家敫桂英，被王魁负盟再娶。妈妈逼奴改嫁金垒，几乎殴辱而死。此恨无由伸诉，只得到海神庙中，把昔日焚香设盟情由，细诉一番。来此已是，不免进去。吓！啊呀大王爷爷吓！奴家敫桂英，与济宁王魁结为夫妇。前年上京应试，一同在神前焚香设誓：若负初心，永坠地狱。谁想他得中状元之后，另娶了韩丞相之女为妻。一旦把奴休了，害得我上天无路，入地无门。为此把昔日焚香设誓情由，细诉一番，望大王爷爷早赐报应㖸！他因功名阻归，寄莱阳淹滞。与奴呵，水萍逢遂谐了匹配。从结发几年间，似水如鱼。我将心儿里没尽藏的倾他，意儿也满载的痴，谁想他暗藏着拖刀之计，一谜价口是心非。他铁铮铮道生同欢笑，啊呀！死同悲，𠮾！到、到如今富易交，贵易妻。啊呀大王爷吓！恁道是薄幸何如？望大王爷勾取那厮到来，与奴对证㖸！这根由天知和那地知。",
      "text_length": 465
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "他赴科场时，与奴呵——",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "一同价在神前焚香誓，他负盟的在刀剑下成粉齑，他惨模糊心瞒昧，一旦的幸登了选魁，他气昂昂忘了貂裘敝，别恋着红妆翠眉，他笑吟吟满将糟糠弃。心儿里兀的不疼杀人也么哥，兀的不疼杀人也么哥。啊呀大王爷吓！恁赤紧的勾取那厮，与咱两个明明白白的对！",
      "text_length": 117
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "大王爷怎么不言不语，不睬着奴家？那厮呵！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "脱布衫",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "他好生的忘筌得鱼，命犯着再娶停妻。那日在大王前言犹在耳，却怎生假装聋佯没些理会？",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "小梁州",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "那厮他欺诳神灵姿意为，全不怕冥法幽司。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "望大王与奴作主，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "浪头",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "一任价一拜一悲啼，肝肠碎！怎不管这情词？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "吓大王爷！大王爷！大王爷不睬奴家，不免去求判官老爹。吓，判官老爹，大王不睬奴家，烦你在大王面前，方便一声，那日焚香设誓，你也是知道的㖸！",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "幺篇",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "自那日从头至尾盟心誓，一一的你却也都知。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "判官老爷与奴方便一声，咳！判官老爷也不睬奴家，不免去求皂隶哥。吓，皂隶哥！牌子哥！判官老爷不肯与奴方便，烦你们在大王跟前禀一声。吓，皂隶哥，牌子哥，呀啐！呀呸！",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "幺篇",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "他们都佯不睬无答对。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "看一堂神圣都不睬奴家，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "敫桂英哈欠。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "神思困倦，不免就在神案前打睡片时，起来再诉！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "幺篇",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "烦絮得神魂颠倒，心恍惚睡魔催。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海神"
      ],
      "text": "鬼判，将她睡魔揭起！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "判官"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海神"
      ],
      "text": "敫桂英听者：要知前世因，今生受者是；欲知后世因，今生作者是。你与王魁善恶相关，怎奈阴阳间隔难以处分。直待你阳寿终时，到我殿庭，明白此事！鬼判，将她扶出殿庭！",
      "text_length": 78
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小鬼"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "海神"
      ],
      "text": "收拾威仪者！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小鬼"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "海神"
      ],
      "text": "大帝乾坤都一照，免教人在暗中行。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "敫桂英哈欠。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "好奇怪，方才朦胧睡去，分明见大王嘱咐，道阴阳间隔，难以处分，直待我阳寿终时，才得与我明白此事。天吓，怎能够阳寿终时，得见大王之面？好奇怪！我的身子怎么到在殿门外了？想是阴官扶我出来的。看殿门已闭，天又昏黑，归又难行，住又难宿，不知什么时候了。",
      "text_length": 121
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "雁叫。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "满庭芳",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "只听得雁声天际，嘹嘹呖呖耿耿凄凄。它那里惨离群任孤飞，只是一生一配，又谁知那有人心的也不念着一夜哎夫妻！他那里绣罗帏只是成双作对，俺在这泥神庙倚砧枕石。寻思起就里，心窝中疼也不疼，满胸臆气也哎不气！",
      "text_length": 99
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "只见那阴风惨惨冲人冷气，最苦是眉锁愁云泪眼双星月暗天迷，似昏沉心乱搅冤家头绪，又谁知万千愁横生梦寐。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "幺篇",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "我只将冤苦伸，恁道是阴阳隔，俺便索须臾做鬼，视死如归心不生悔，现如今无靠依难凭据，只是不存不济，挨得我疼无声，哭得咱眼枯双泪！",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "且住，方才大王爷嘱咐，毕竟要我死。我若不死，怎得见王魁？只是这个所在，将什么东西自尽呢？吖，我有罗帕在此，将它做个了身之计罢！吓，啊呀罗帕吓罗帕！",
      "text_length": 73
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "可惜你千丝万缕，织成一段离愁，不知前世甚冤仇，今日将咱了首。就里恓惶知否？眼中血泪难收，从今与你两情休，啊呀留在咽喉左右！",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "快活三",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "这些事，生独自倒不如死疼棲。假饶是冤家啊呀不同妻，啊呀王魁吓！我断断不放恁与那新夫人和她做一处！",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "朝天子",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "我把红颜玉姿，掩黄沙白骨，霎时间辞人世。这的是下场头夫妻们恩义，香罗帕做仇敌。只是花褪香枯，可也脂抛粉坠，啊呀王魁吓，我向前行你也难回避。啊呀桂英吓，哭咱一会！啊呀王魁恁那负心的贼吓，我骂，骂他一回！啊呀天吓，我这、这的是永决了咽喉——",
      "text_length": 118
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "朝天子",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "气！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "敫桂英"
      ],
      "text": "罢！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902157_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902157",
      "scene_id": "70902157_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "敫桂英下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}